  "body": "I would like to build a mobile dapp that can sense a user's movement or location change.\r\n\r\nCan I build a dapp with truffle and react and access the phone's native features such as geolocation or phone movement?\r\n\r\nCould I make an ionic native app and use it through status so that the user can send ether payments and have access to device native features?\r\n\r\nI found the following which suggests that I can make an ionic app and use it with status to have both device native features and ether payment.\r\nhttps://ethereum.stackexchange.com/questions/18461/how-can-dapps-work-on-smartphones",
